PR Title: (hot)/ FEAPP-420: Allow customer notification via WhatsApp

DESCRIPTION: 
Customers have been requesting the ability to get
notified about product updates via their WhatsApp number.

WHAT:
Creating a optional button allow notification to whatsapp number also.

WHY:
This mode of notification is optional, but if specified, should cause
notifications to go out both on their emails as well as WhatsApp numbers.

NOTES:
We need to ship this feature to the customer in the Q3 as our results can be
influenced by this feature.

PR REVIEWERS:
Tapas Das
Jayasurya
Nireeksha
